%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20India%E2%80%99s%20North-South%20Divide%20a%20Challenge%20to%20Hindutva%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F12163456%2F49552290-black_6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuddenly%2C%20the%20North-South%20divide%20in%20India%20has%20become%20a%20political%20hot%20potato.%20The%20main%20claim%20rests%20on%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20North%2C%20citizens%20in%20the%20South%20are%20better%20educated%2C%20economically%20better%20off%20and%20are%20marked%20by%20a%20less%20antagonistic%20history%20of%20cultural%20assimilation.%20The%20blunt%20political%20assessment%20being%20that%20the%20entire%20southern%20region%20is%20a%20naturally%20outside%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20Bhratiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20its%20majoritarian%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20what%20if%20the%20North-South%20divide%20actually%20points%20to%20a%20much%20deeper%20struggle%20between%20two%20competing%20visions%20for%20India%3F%20Consequently%2C%20the%20mandate%20from%20the%20general%20elections%20of%202024%20will%20be%20but%20a%20mere%20event%20within%20a%20larger%20societal%20upheaval.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20election%20mandates%20can%20easily%20turn%20sour.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20(INC)%20led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%E2%80%99s%20(UPA)%20comfortable%20win%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20of%202009%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20proves%20the%20point.%20Between%202010%20and%202014%2C%20not%20only%20did%20the%20INC%20fail%20to%20draw%20the%20links%20between%20emerging%20digital%20technologies%20and%20politics%20but%20lost%20the%20ability%20to%20gauge%20the%20popular%20mood%20in%20India%2C%20especially%20amongst%20the%20upper%20castes.%20To%20be%20fair%20though%2C%20those%20very%20same%20years%20witnessed%20tectonic%20political%20shifts%20across%20the%20world%20with%20several%20countries%20embracing%20%E2%80%98right%20wing%20populism%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20contemporary%20populist%20turn%2C%20in%20a%20nutshell%2C%20refers%20to%20so%20called%20%E2%80%98strong%20leaders%E2%80%99%20gaming%20liberal%20democracies%20by%20weaponising%20majoritarian%20and%20supremacist%20identity%20politics.%20But%20critical%20to%20these%20populist%20triumphs%20was%20the%20maturation%20of%20social%20media%2C%20big%20data%20and%20increased%20internet%20and%20mobile%20penetration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20347px)%2085vw%2C%20347px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16124428%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-12.44.08-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22347%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16124428%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-12.44.08-PM.png%20678w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16124428%2FScreenshot-2024-01-16-at-12.44.08-PM-206x300.png%20206w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693160%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDilip%20Hiro%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Age%20of%20Aspiration%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20New%20Press%20(2015)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInvestigative%20journalist%20Dilip%20Hiro%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Age%20of%20Aspiration%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2018)%20notes%20how%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20was%20alert%20to%20the%20political%20significance%20of%20data%20and%20even%20set%20up%20its%20first%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20unit%20in%20as%20early%20as%202010%2C%20called%20the%20National%20Digital%20Operations%20Cell%20(N-DOC).%20This%20dedicated%20IT%20outfit%2C%20soon%20enough%2C%20assembled%20a%20large%20database%20and%20during%20the%202014%20Indian%20general%20elections%20specially%20deployed%20a%20cyber%20army%20to%20impact%20155%20urban%20constituencies%2C%20labeled%20as%20%E2%80%98digital%20seats%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20embrace%20of%20IT%20also%20masterfully%20complemented%20the%20turnaround%20of%20the%20Indian%20corporate%20houses%20and%20in%20drawing%20support%20from%20the%20non-resident%20Indian%20diaspora%20through%20the%20Overseas%20Friends%20of%20the%20BJP%20(OFBJP).%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%98s%202014%20election%20campaign%20juggernaut%20ended%20up%20outspending%20the%20ruling%20INC%20by%204%3A1.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20issues%2C%20development%20and%20corruption%20dominated%20the%20messaging%20for%20the%202014%20general%20elections%20and%20national%20security%20won%20the%20votes%20in%202019%2C%20it%20is%20becoming%20apparent%20that%20the%20BJP%20intends%20to%20win%202024%20mainly%20on%20the%20plank%20of%20Hindutva%3A%20broadly%20defined%20as%20an%20ideology%20that%20seeks%20to%20establish%20the%20cultural%20and%20political%20hegemony%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nationalism%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%E2%80%99s%20imagined%20social%20coalition%20is%20supposedly%20made%20up%20of%20all%20castes%20and%20groups%20that%20have%20historically%20evolved%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20Hinduism.%20According%20to%20the%202011%20census%20of%20India%2C%20close%20to%2080%20%25%20of%20the%20population%20identifies%20as%20Hindu.%20The%20BJP%20on%20its%20own%20received%2031%20%25%20of%20the%20votes%20in%202014%20and%20which%20jumped%20to%2038.4%20%25%20of%20the%20total%20votes%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections.%20And%2C%20from%20the%20standpoint%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20an%20even%20greater%20augmentation%20of%20numbers%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20realised%20in%20the%20coming%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20here%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20INC%2C%20at%20the%20height%20of%20its%20political%20sway%2C%20rested%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98core%20social%20coalition%E2%80%99%20that%20comprised%20upper%20castes%20(nowadays%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20general%20category)%2C%20Dalits%20or%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20various%20communities%20listed%20as%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20and%20minorities%20(Muslims%2C%20Christians%2C%20Sikhs).%20This%20social%20coalition%20of%20the%20INC%20along%20with%20other%20caste%20combinations%20at%20the%20regional%20level%20proved%20fairly%20durable%20from%20the%201950s%20up%20to%20the%20late%201980s%20and%20was%20sustained%20with%20notions%20about%20the%20mixed%20economy%2C%20secularism%20and%20the%20ethos%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20From%20the%20mid-1990s%2C%20however%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20robust%20embrace%20of%20economic%20liberalisation%2C%20the%20INC%E2%80%99s%20core%20social%20coalition%20began%20to%20wobble%20and%20suffered%20its%20lowest%20with%20the%20stunning%20en%20masse%20exit%20of%20the%20upper%20castes%20into%20the%20eager%20arms%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%202014.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0BJP%20and%20a%20problem%20called%20Hindutva%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20spectacular%20electoral%20successes%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20managing%20a%20social%20coalition%20on%20the%20appeal%20of%20Hindutva%20still%20remains%20a%20fraught%20project.%20For%20one%2C%20as%20Pankaj%20Kumar%20in%20a%20recent%20piece%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reminds%20us%2C%20creating%20a%20social%20and%20cultural%20unity%20around%20%E2%80%98hindu-ness%2C%20nationalism%20and%20development%E2%80%99%20greatly%20depends%20on%20how%20material%20contradictions%20between%20different%20castes%20are%20hidden%20from%20sight.%20Kumar%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20spells%20out%20how%20the%20BJPs%20success%20in%20recruiting%20subaltern%20castes%20comprising%20the%20Other%20Backwards%20Castes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Extreme%20Backwards%20Castes%20(EBCs)%2C%20SCs%20and%20the%20STs%20depends%20greatly%20on%20%E2%80%98culturalisation%E2%80%99%3A%20side%20stepping%20caste%20hierarchy%20and%20domination%20by%20creating%20belonging%20and%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym-300x194.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym-1024x662.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684198%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22776%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20supporters%20hold%20up%20Modi%20posters.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20culturalisation%2C%20the%20second%20strategy%20for%20the%20BJP%20involves%20transforming%20the%20subaltern%20castes%20into%20%3Cem%3Elabharatis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(beneficiaries)%20of%20various%20schemes%20that%20involve%20the%20transfer%20of%20cash%20or%20kind%20(food%20grains%20and%20other%20subsistence%20items)%2C%20just%20before%20voting.%20For%20public%20policy%20researcher%20Yamini%20Aiyar%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20however%2C%20these%20%E2%80%98labharati%20schemes%E2%80%99%20neither%20foster%20citizen-rights%20nor%20strengthen%20public%20services%20such%20as%20education%2C%20health%20or%20nutrition.%20Instead%2C%20the%20poorest%20across%20the%20class%20and%20caste%20spectrum%20get%20politically%20demobilised%20and%20are%20rendered%20into%20passive%20recipients%20of%20state%20largesse%20through%20the%20rubric%20of%20public%20welfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20culturalisation%2C%20labharti-ism%20and%20the%20BJPs%20powerful%20organisational%20capacity%20have%20ensured%20a%20string%20of%20electoral%20wins%2C%20tensions%20remain.%20Particularly%20when%20dealing%20with%20the%20challenge%20of%20social%20justice.%20Take%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20November%202022%20judgement%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20upheld%20reservations%20for%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Sections%20(EWS)%2C%20introduced%20through%20the%20Constitutional%20103%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erd%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202019.%20Strikingly%20enough%2C%20the%20judgment%20excluded%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20EBC%20and%20OBCs%20from%20availing%20of%20the%20EWS%20quota%2C%20even%20though%20these%20castes%20comprise%20some%20of%20the%20most%20economically%20disadvantaged.%20In%20effect%2C%20the%20EWS%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20captive%20preserve%20for%20the%20upper%20castes.%20The%20obvious%20political%20implication%20being%20that%20social%20justice%20involves%20zero-sum%20outcomes.%20The%20gains%20of%20one%20caste%20can%20only%20happen%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20another%20caste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20realisation%20that%20all%20castes%20are%20not%20equally%20placed%20on%20the%20grand%20stage%20of%20Hindutva%20also%20explains%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ambivalence%20on%20the%20caste%20census.%20A%20census%20that%20could%20be%20particularly%20troubling%20in%20revealing%20the%20intensity%20of%20caste-based%20and%20caste-caused%20inequality%20that%20runs%20across%20a%20range%20of%20socio-economic%20indicators.%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey%20data%20released%20in%202023%2C%20for%20example%2C%20not%20only%20laid%20bare%20how%20skewed%20economic%20opportunity%20and%20access%20to%20social%20capital%20was%20amongst%20the%20different%20castes%20and%20communities%20but%2C%20more%20pointedly%2C%20in%20the%20inadvertent%20implications%20from%20the%20percentages.%20If%20one%20added%20numbers%20comprising%20the%20OBCs%20(27.12%25)%2C%20EBC%20(36.03%25)%2C%20SC%20(19.65%25)%20and%20the%20ST%20(1.68%25)%2C%20then%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20a%20total%20of%C2%A0%2081.47%20%25%20of%20the%20population%20could%20be%20mobilised%20under%20the%20social%20justice%20platform%20rather%20than%20be%20drawn%20into%20the%20folds%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fneed-of-the-hour-a-selfie-called-caste-census-india-must-confront-its-truth%5C%22%3ENeed%20of%20the%20Hour%3A%20A%20Selfie%20Called%20Caste%20Census%20%E2%80%93%20India%20Must%20Confront%20its%20Truth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20upper%20caste%20interests%20and%20their%20anxieties%20colour%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20project.%20What%20is%20widely%20touted%20as%20a%20quest%20to%20unite%20the%20%E2%80%98embattled%E2%80%99%20Hindu%20identity%20involves%2C%20in%20practice%2C%20the%20dexterous%20and%20troubled%20politics%20for%20assembling%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20solidarity%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20social%20pyramid%2C%20where%20the%20upper%20castes%20or%20general%20category%20elites%20are%20expected%20to%20dominate%20the%20apex%20while%20the%20other%20castes%20are%20%E2%80%98ritually%20adjusted%E2%80%99%20within%20a%20descending%20order.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20securing%20the%20top%20position%20and%20not%20allowing%20the%20pyramid%20to%20crumble%20is%20no%20easy%20task%20either%20%E2%80%93%20an%20inherent%20fragility%20that%20Ravinder%20Kaur%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20monograph%3Cem%3E%20Brand%20New%20Nation%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2020)%20compellingly%20alerts%20us%20to.%20Kaur%20notes%20how%20the%20INC%20suffered%20stiff%20upper%20caste%20disquiet%20just%20as%20neoliberal%20globalisation%20policies%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20working%20in%20their%20favour.%20Following%20a%20robust%20push%20via%20new%20market%20logics%20for%20rural%20to%20urban%20migration%20from%20the%20mid-1990s%20onwards%2C%20the%20upper%20castes%20unexpectedly%20found%20themselves%20jostling%20against%20the%20urbanised%20aspirations%20from%20incoming%20waves%20of%20SC%20and%20OBC%20rural%20migrants.%20And%20as%20decent%20middle-class%20jobs%20became%20scarcer%2C%20upper%20castes%20anxieties%20became%20even%20more%20palpable%20over%20their%20growing%20vulnerability%20to%20the%20constitutionally%20guaranteed%20system%20of%20the%20universal%20franchise%20(one%20person%20one%20vote).%20That%20is%2C%20the%20belief%20that%20their%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20cultural%20dominance%20might%20not%20prevent%20them%20from%20becoming%20politically%20marginal%20within%20India.%20This%20widely%20perceived%20political%20irrelevance%20from%20the%20politics%20of%20numbers%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20story%20that%20had%20already%20played%20out%20in%20the%20South%2C%20not%20as%20anxiety%20and%20fear%20but%20as%20fact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20North-South%20divide%20and%20the%20INC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20innumerable%20subaltern%20caste%20struggles%20for%20social%20emancipation%20and%20economic%20upliftment%20have%20reverberated%20across%20South%20India%2C%20with%20Dalit%20and%20tribal%20movements%20still%20bitterly%20fighting%2C%20even%20to%20this%20day%2C%20over%20their%20continued%20oppression.%20What%20remains%20a%20striking%20feature%20in%20the%20social%20landscape%20is%20the%20dramatic%20transformation%20of%20several%20erstwhile%20peasant%20or%20Shudra%20communities%20into%20%E2%80%98dominant%20castes%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20349px)%2085vw%2C%20349px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16124731%2F81eSswdFFxL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22349%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16124731%2F81eSswdFFxL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20608w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16124731%2F81eSswdFFxL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-182x300.jpg%20182w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693162%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22574%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHarish%20Damodaran%2C%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20New%20Capitalists%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EPalgrave%20Macmillan%20(2008)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarish%20Damodaran%20in%20his%20award-winning%20book%20%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20New%20Capitalists%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2008)%20meticulously%20documents%20how%20former%20cultivating%20castes%20such%20as%20the%20Kammas%2C%20Reddys%2C%20Rajus%2C%20Nadars%2C%20Kongunad%20Naidus%2C%20Gounders%20and%20the%20Ezhavas%20adopted%20an%20entrepreneurial%20route%2C%20throughout%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20to%20set%20up%20factories%20and%20inevitably%20enabling%20their%20entry%20into%20the%20corporate%20boardroom.%20Their%20businesses%20spanned%20a%20huge%20spectrum%3A%20manufacturing%2C%20food%20processing%2C%20engineering%20goods%2C%20construction%20of%20dams%20and%20public%20highways%2C%20telecom%2C%20ports%2C%20mines%20and%20even%20investing%20in%20film%20production.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20subsequent%20writings%2C%20Damodaran%20describes%20the%20years%20between%201991%20and%202011%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20closest%20tryst%20with%20%E2%80%98free-market%20entrepreneurial%20capitalism%E2%80%99.%20Not%20only%20was%20the%20overall%20environment%20one%20of%20optimism%20and%20conducive%20for%20risk-taking%20but%20it%20also%20prodded%20diverse%20ethnic%20and%20caste%20backgrounds%20to%20take%20up%20entrepreneurship.%20The%20rise%20of%20South%20India%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20castes%2C%20moreover%2C%20was%20also%20coterminous%20with%20coalition%20politics%20at%20the%20Union%20level%20and%20vibrant%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202014%2C%20however%2C%20the%20swagger%20and%20shine%20of%20these%20%E2%80%98Andhra-preneurs%E2%80%99%20has%20all%20but%20faded.%20A%20raft%20of%20shock%20and%20awe%20policies%20such%20as%20demonetisation%2C%20the%20hurried%20implementation%20of%20the%20GST%20(Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax)%20and%20the%20Insolvency%20and%20Bankruptcy%20Code%C2%A0(IBC)%20has%20undermined%20the%20competitive%20edge%20of%20many%20medium%20and%20small%20businesses.%20For%20journalist%20M.%20Rajashekar%2C%20India%20Inc%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20been%20brutally%20winnowed%20through%20%E2%80%98a%20giant%20fire%20sale%E2%80%99%2C%20wherein%20debt%20strapped%20businesses%20have%20been%20picked%20up%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20buyers%20at%20less%20than%20competitive%20prices%2C%20causing%20the%20%E2%80%98largest%20change%20in%20ownership%20patterns%20since%20independence%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20To%20several%2C%20this%20post-2014%20emergence%20of%20muscular%20monopolies%2C%20rigged%20markets%20and%20the%20run%20of%20oligopolies%2C%20ineluctably%20harkens%20India%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20the%20previous%20domination%20by%20%E2%80%98Bania-Brahmin%E2%80%99%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20amidst%20what%20some%20would%20term%20a%20counter-revolution%20of%20sorts%2C%20that%20the%20INC%E2%80%99s%20decisive%20wins%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20state%20elections%20opens%20the%20possibility%20for%20reconfiguring%20itself%20as%20the%20party%20of%20the%20OBC%20and%20dominant%20castes.%20And%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20social%20pyramid%2C%20the%20metaphor%20for%20the%20INC%20can%20be%20the%20image%20of%20a%20wheel%20with%20the%20dominant%20castes%2FOBCs%20holding%20the%20centre%20and%20spokes%20radiating%20outwards%20to%20meaningfully%20connect%20with%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20minorities%20and%20an%20array%20of%20other%20political%20groupings.%20This%20socially%20rejigged%20INC%20can%20then%20choose%20to%20be%20realistic%20about%20their%20previous%20equations%20with%20the%20upper%20castes%2C%20even%20as%20they%20provide%20the%20intellectual%20heft%20to%20transition%20its%20newly%20assembled%20OBC-led%20alliance%20system%20from%20earlier%20regional%20moorings%20to%20one%20that%20is%20prepping%20for%20a%20national%20role.%20That%20is%2C%20transform%20the%20OBCs%20and%20dominant%20castes%20from%20being%20regional%20satraps%20into%20a%20pan-India%20leadership%2C%20a%20preserve%20that%20was%20held%20only%20by%20the%20upper%20castes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%2C%20two%20competing%20visions%20have%20been%20thrown%20up.%20On%20the%20right%20is%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20balance%20its%20social%20pyramid%20by%20principally%20defending%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20upper%20castes.%20Though%20the%20%E2%80%98ritual%20adjustment%E2%80%99%20of%20other%20castes%20within%20the%20folds%20of%20Hindutva%20have%20produced%20several%20stunning%20electoral%20wins%2C%20these%20arrangements%20are%20inherently%20fragile%20and%20prone%20to%20crisis%20as%20it%20depends%20greatly%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20sustain%20strong%20man%20politics%20and%20continually%20ensure%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20backsliding.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20along%20the%20center-left%20spectrum%2C%20a%20socially%20reconfigured%20INC%2C%20as%20the%20party%20of%20the%20dominant%20castes%2FOBC%2C%20is%20now%20ideally%20positioned%20to%20pursue%20social%20justice%20as%20an%20inclusive%20nation-making%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurning%20the%20wheel%20for%20social%20justice%20and%20inclusion%2C%20however%2C%20will%20greatly%20depend%20on%20how%20the%20INC%20can%20galvanise%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20for%20bringing%20about%20change%20through%20democratic%20negotiations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpromise-to-bring-peace-says-rahul-gandhi-as-he-kicks-off-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-manipur%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%20(the%20theme%20unsurprisingly%20being%20Nyay%20or%20justice)%20clearly%20tells%20us%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20Indian%20general%20elections%20of%202024%20will%20be%20but%20a%20mere%20blip%20within%20a%20larger%20protracted%20battle.%20It%20is%20no%20mystery%20that%20social%20justice%20and%20Hindutva%20are%20hurtling%20towards%20a%20definitive%20show%20down.%20A%20battle%20with%20no%20middle%20ground%20and%20the%20taking%20of%20prisoners%2C%20most%20unlikely.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ERohan%20D%E2%80%99Souza%20teaches%20at%20the%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Asian%20and%20African%20Area%20Studies%2C%20Kyoto%20University%2C%20Japan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705394157000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F12163456%2F49552290-black_6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-indias-north-south-divide-a-challenge-to-hindutva%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20no%20mystery%20that%20social%20justice%20and%20Hindutva%20are%20hurtling%20towards%20a%20definitive%20show%20down.%20A%20battle%20with%20no%20middle%20ground%20and%20the%20taking%20of%20prisoners%2C%20most%20unlikely.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-indias-north-south-divide-a-challenge-to-hindu