2%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20Watches%20could%20lose%20this%20one%20feature%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705391507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106892061%2Cimgsize-2270775.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fapple-watch-series-9-and-watch-ultra-2-could-lose-this-one-feature%2Farticleshow%2F106892145.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20presented%20a%20software%20workaround%20to%20bypass%20the%20dispute%20and%20is%20awaiting%20a%20ruling%20from%20the%20ITC.%20If%20ruled%20in%20Apple's%20favor%2C%20they%20can%20continue%20selling%20unmodified%20versions%20of%20the%20Apple%20watches.%20The%20hearing%20will%20determine%20the%20next%20steps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ABHINAV%20KAUSTUBH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fapple-watch-series-9-and-watch-ultra-2-could-lose-this-one-feature%2Farticleshow%2F106892145.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20To%20Complete%20KYC%20Before%20Jan%2031%20To%20Avoid%20FASTag%20Deactivation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Highway%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20be%20deactivating%20those%20FASTags%20for%20which%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(KYC)%20is%20not%20done.%20The%20deadline%20for%20the%20same%20is%20January%2031%2C%20the%20highways%20authority%20further%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20'One%20Vehicle%2C%20One%20FASTag'%20initiative%20that%20aims%20to%20discourage%20use%20of%20single%20FASTag%20for%20multiple%20vehicles%20or%20linking%20multiple%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20tool%20to%20a%20single%20vehicle.%20To%20avoid%20inconvenience%2C%20the%20statement%20said%20users%20must%20ensure%20that%20KYC%20of%20their%20latest%20FASTag%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20the%20latest%20FASTag%20account%20shall%20remain%20active%20as%20previous%20tags%20will%20be%20deactivated%2Fblacklisted%20after%2031st%20January%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20did%20NHAI%20take%20this%20action%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20highways%20body%20said%20it%20took%20the%20initiative%20after%20it%20was%20informed%20that%20more%20than%20one%20FASTag%20has%20been%20issued%20for%20a%20particular%20vehicle%20and%20FASTags%20being%20issued%20without%20KYC%20in%20violation%20of%20RBI's%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NHAI%20also%20said%20that%20FASTags%20are%20sometimes%20deliberately%20not%20fixed%20on%20the%20windscreen%20of%20the%20vehicle%2C%20resulting%20in%20unnecessary%20delays%20at%20toll%20plazas%20and%20causing%20inconvenience%20to%20people%20using%20national%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20FASTag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20pre-paid%20tag%20facility%20for%20vehicles%20that%20allows%20non-stop%20movement%20of%20traffic%20without%20having%20to%20wait%20at%20the%20toll%20plazas.%20It's%20a%20revolutionary%20step%20that%20uses%20Radio-Frequency%20Identification%20or%20RFID%20technology%20and%20enables%20automatic%20deduction%20of%20the%20toll%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20steps%20to%20digitise%20toll%20collection%2C%20the%20central%20government%20made%20FASTags%20mandatory%20from%20February%2015%2C%202021%20saying%20that%20any%20vehicle%20not%20fitted%20with%20it%20will%20be%20charged%20double%20the%20toll%20at%20electronic%20toll%20plazas%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20purchase%20a%20FASTag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sticker-type%20RFID%20document%20can%20be%20purchased%20from%20over%2028%2C000%20Point-of-Sale%20(POS)%20locations%20set%20up%20by%20various%20banks%2C%20national%20highways%20fee%20plazas%2C%20Regional%20Transport%20Offices%2C%20common%20service%20centres%2C%20transport%20hubs%2C%20bank%20branches%20and%20petrol%20pumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20affixed%20on%20the%20windscreen%20of%20a%20car%20so%20that%20RFID%20readers%20installed%20at%20toll%20plazas%20can%20read%20it%20and%20deduct%20the%20required%20amount%20automatically.%20FASTags%20promote%20digital%20payments%20and%20avoid%20physical%20currency%20at%20toll%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20have%20your%20own%20KYC%20documents%20to%20purchase%20a%20FASTag%2C%20either%20online%20or%20offline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20KYC%20documents%20needed%20for%20buying%20FASTag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20documents%20include%20registration%20certificate%20(RC)%20of%20a%20car%2C%20identity%2C%20address%20proof%20and%20a%20passport%20size%20photo.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20original%20as%20well%20as%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20KYC%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20check%20FASTag%20status%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20can%20visit%20a%20dedicated%20website%20https%3A%2F%2Ffastag.ihmcl.com%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20login%2C%20details%20like%20registered%20mobile%20number%20and%20password%20are%20needed.%20Authorisation%20will%20be%20done%20through%20OTP.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20logging%20in%2C%20navigate%20to%20dashboard%2C%20where%20a%20section%20called%20%26quot%3BMy%20Profile%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20available.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20will%20show%20a%20user's%20KYC%20status%20and%20profile%20details%20submitted%20through%20the%20registration%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20do%20if%20KYC%20is%20pending%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20Profile%20section%2C%20a%20sub-section%20called%20KYC%20will%20allow%20users%20to%20update%20their%20KYC.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20will%20need%20to%20fill%20various%20fields%20by%20submitting%20required%20identity%20and%20address%20proof%20documents.%20A%20passport-sized%20photo%20will%20also%20be%20required.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20clicking%20on%20Submit%2C%20users%20need%20to%20check%20and%20confirm%20the%20declaration.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20clicking%20on%20Proceed%2C%20KYC%20verification%20process%20will%20be%20completed%20by%20submitting%20the%20required%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705391340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F2ps7mplk_fastag_650x400_25_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffastags-with-incomplete-kyc-to-be-deactivated-after-jan-31-heres-how-to-avoid-that-4872348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Highway%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20be%20deactivating%20those%20FASTags%20for%20which%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(KYC)%20is%20not%20done.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffastags-with-incomplete-kyc-to-be-deactivated-after-jan-31-heres-how-to-avoid-that-4872348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffastags-with-incomplete-kyc-to-be-deactivated-after-jan-31-heres-how-to-avoid-that-4872348%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffastags-with-incomplete-kyc-to-be-deactivated-after-jan-31-heres-how-to-avoid-that-4872348%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Disease%20X%3F%20How%20Scientists%20Are%20Preparing%20For%20The%20Next%20Pandemic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20like%20something%20Elon%20Musk%20might%20have%20cooked%20up%3A%20%26quot%3BDisease%20X.%26quot%3B%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20term%20was%20coined%20years%20ago%20as%20a%20way%20of%20getting%20scientists%20to%20work%20on%20medical%20countermeasures%20for%20unknown%20infectious%20threats%20-%20novel%20coronaviruses%20like%20the%20one%20that%20causes%20Covid-19%2C%20for%20example%20-%20instead%20of%20just%20known%20ones%2C%20like%20the%20Ebola%20virus.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20encourage%20the%20development%20of%20platform%20technologies%2C%20including%20vaccines%2C%20drug%20therapies%20and%20diagnostic%20tests%2C%20that%20could%20be%20rapidly%20adapted%20and%20deployed%20in%20response%20to%20an%20array%20of%20future%20outbreaks%20with%20epidemic%20or%20pandemic%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20What%20is%20'Disease%20X%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20somewhat%20mysterious%20name%20for%20an%20illness%20caused%20by%20a%20currently%20unknown%2C%20yet%20serious%20microbial%20threat.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organization%20added%20Disease%20X%20in%202017%20to%20a%20short%20list%20of%20pathogens%20deemed%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20research%2C%20alongside%20known%20killers%20like%20Severe%20Acute%20Respiratory%20Syndrome%20(SARS)%20and%20Ebola.%20The%20issue%20made%20it%20onto%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20with%20WHO%20Director%20General%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%20joining%20other%20health%20officials%20to%20discuss%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovid-19%2C%20caused%20by%20a%20novel%20coronavirus%2C%20was%20an%20example%20of%20a%20Disease%20X%20when%20it%20touched%20off%20the%20pandemic%20at%20the%20end%20of%202019.%20The%20vast%20reservoir%20of%20viruses%20circulating%20in%20wildlife%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20likely%20source%20of%20more%20such%20diseases.%20That's%20because%20of%20their%20potential%20to%20spill%20over%20and%20infect%20other%20species%2C%20including%20humans%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20an%20infection%20against%20which%20people%20will%20have%20no%20immunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20What's%20the%20point%20of%20studying%20Disease%20X%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20WHO%20puts%20it%2C%20it's%20to%20%26quot%3Benable%20early%20cross-cutting%20R%26amp%3BD%20preparedness%20that%20is%20also%20relevant%26quot%3B%20for%20an%20unknown%20disease.%20The%20humanitarian%20crisis%20sparked%20by%20the%202014-2016%20Ebola%20epidemic%20in%20West%20Africa%20was%20a%20wake%20up%20call.%20Despite%20decades%20of%20research%2C%20there%20were%20no%20products%20ready%20to%20deploy%20in%20time%20to%20save%20more%20than%2011%2C000%20lives.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20WHO%20created%20an%20R%26amp%3BD%20Blueprint%20to%20accelerate%20development%20of%20a%20range%20of%20tools%20for%20%26quot%3Bpriority%20diseases.%26quot%3B%20The%20current%20list%20includes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECovid-19%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECrimean-Congo%20hemorrhagic%20fever%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEbola%20virus%20disease%20and%20Marburg%20virus%20disease%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELassa%20fever%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMiddle%20East%20respiratory%20syndrome%20(MERS)%20and%20SARS%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENipah%20and%20henipaviral%20diseases%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERift%20Valley%20fever%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EZika%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDisease%20X%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20How's%20the%20research%20for%20the%20next%20pandemic%20going%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20just%20326%20days%20from%20the%20release%20of%20the%20genetic%20sequence%20of%20the%20SARS-CoV-2%20virus%20to%20the%20authorization%20of%20the%20first%20Covid%20vaccine%2C%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20the%20work%20done%20since%202017%20in%20preparation%20for%20Disease%20X.%20Now%20groups%20like%20the%20Coalition%20for%20Epidemic%20Preparedness%20Innovations%2C%20or%20CEPI%2C%20are%20supporting%20rapid%20response%20vaccine%20platforms%20that%20could%20develop%20new%20immunizations%20within%20100%20days%20of%20a%20virus%20with%20pandemic%20potential%20emerging%20under%20a%20%243.5%20billion%20plan.%20Other%20efforts%20underway%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUpdating%20the%20International%20Health%20Regulations%20and%20developing%20a%20new%20global%20agreement%20to%20protect%20the%20world%20from%20future%20emergencies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20new%20fund%2C%20approved%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20for%20pandemic%20prevention%2C%20preparedness%20and%20response.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20WHO%20Hub%20for%20Pandemic%20and%20Epidemic%20Intelligence%20in%20Berlin%20that%20aims%20to%20speed%20access%20to%20key%20data%2C%20and%20develop%20analytic%20tools%20and%20predictive%20models%20to%20assess%20potential%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Global%20Virome%20Project%20that%20aims%20to%20discover%20zoonotic%20viral%20threats%20and%20stop%20future%20pandemics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20%245%20billion%20US%20government%20initiative%20to%20develop%20next-generation%20vaccines%20and%20treatments%20for%20Covid-19%2C%20called%20Project%20NextGen.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%24262.5%20million%20in%20funding%20for%20a%20US%20national%20network%20for%20detecting%20and%20responding%20more%20efficiently%20to%20public%20health%20emergencies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEstablishment%20of%20global%20center%20for%20pandemic%20therapeutics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20numerous%20challenges%20threaten%20to%20undermine%20these%20efforts%2C%20including%20depleted%20and%20weakened%20health%20systems%2C%20a%20growing%20anti-science%20movement%20that%20has%20increased%20vaccine%20hesitancy%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20governments%20to%20eventually%20deprioritize%20funding%20for%20outbreak%20detection%20and%20preparedness%20as%20perceived%20risks%20dissipate%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705391280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftrsj4j7g_disease-x_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-is-disease-x-how-scientists-are-preparing-for-the-next-pandemic-4872