s%20contribution%2C%20and%20lauds%20director%20Vidhu%20Vinod%20Chopra.%20Despite%20the%20film's%20October%20release%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20draw%20attention%2C%20earning%20over%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20in%20its%2012th%20weekend%20and%20accumulating%20a%20box%20office%20collection%20of%20Rs%2055.30%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2F12th-fail-alia-bhatt-is-in-awe-of-vikrant-massey-calls-the-movie-too-too-too-beautiful%2Farticleshow%2F106890903.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India%20Should%20Let%20Maldives%20Learn%20The%20Cost%20Of%20A%20Chinese%20Embrace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20bringing%20Delhi-Male%20ties%20from%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20precipice.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20has%20doubled%20down%20with%20a%20rhetorical%20escalation%20after%20his%20return%20from%20China.%20Even%20as%20his%20ministers%20were%20passing%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Muizzu%2C%20during%20his%20five-day%20state%20visit%20to%20China%20last%20week%2C%20described%20China%20one%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bclosest%20allies%20and%20development%20partners%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%20projects%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20significant%20infrastructure%20projects%20witnessed%20in%20Maldivian%20history.%26quot%3B%20After%20coming%20back%20from%20China%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20India%20by%20suggesting%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20%5Bthe%20Maldives%5D%20may%20be%20small%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20give%20you%20the%20license%20to%20bully%20us.%26quot%3B%20And%20then%20came%20the%20ultimatum%20from%20his%20government%20that%20New%20Delhi%20withdraw%20its%20military%20presence%20from%20the%20archipelago%20nation%20before%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20none%20of%20this%20should%20have%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20Muizzu%20had%20campaigned%20on%20an%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out%26quot%3B%20platform%20and%20had%20been%20a%20votary%20of%20strong%20ties%20with%20China.%20After%20taking%20over%20the%20Presidency%20of%20the%20Maldives%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20he%20had%20called%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20troops%20which%20are%20around%2080%20in%20number%2C%20primarily%20positioned%20there%20for%20humanitarian%20and%20disaster%20relief%20as%20well%20as%20to%20maintain%20and%20operate%20two%20rescue%20and%20reconnaissance%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornier%20aircraft%20gifted%20by%20India%20to%20the%20Maldives.%20Muizzu%20has%20tried%20to%20mobilise%20his%20domestic%20political%20base%20by%20targeting%20India%20and%20has%20found%20support%20among%20Islamic%20hardliners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20snub%20to%20India%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20first%20visit%20Turkey%20and%20then%20China%20for%20bilateral%20engagements.%20His%20government%20decided%20not%20to%20renew%20a%20pact%20for%20a%20hydrographic%20survey%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20seawaters%20with%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20Colombo%20Security%20Conclave%20last%20December%2C%20in%20which%20it%20is%20a%20member%20state%20along%20with%20India%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Mauritius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20China%20visit%2C%20the%20two%20nations%20signed%20a%20comprehensive%20strategic%20cooperative%20partnership%20and%20Muizzu%20exhorted%20China%20to%20try%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20number%20one%20market%20for%20the%20Maldives%20by%20sending%20more%20tourists.%20He%20underlined%20his%20administration's%20commitment%20to%20the%20quick%20implementation%20of%20the%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20(FTA)%20signed%20with%20China%2C%20a%20pact%20that%20this%20predecessor%20President%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20was%20reluctant%20to%20implement.%20And%20at%20a%20time%20when%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20world%20is%20getting%20disillusioned%20with%20the%20BRI%20and%20China's%20own%20economy%20is%20facing%20headwinds%2C%20Muizzu%20sang%20paeans%20to%20the%20BRI%20projects%20and%20their%20importance%20for%20the%20Maldivian%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20all%20of%20this%2C%20New%20Delhi's%20official%20reaction%20to%20Muizzu's%20provocations%20has%20been%20sober%20and%20mature.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Muizzu%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20COP28%20World%20Climate%20Action%20Summit%20in%20Doha%20that%20a%20high-level%20committee%20was%20formed%20to%20try%20to%20find%20a%20compromise.%20India%20kept%20its%20cool%20even%20when%20the%20ministers%20in%20the%20Muizzu%20government%20made%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20social%20media%20blew%20up.%20And%20recently%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20asserted%20that%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20is%20politics%3A%20and%20it%20cannot%20be%20guaranteed%20that%20in%20every%20country%2C%20every%20day%2C%20everybody%20will%20support%20us%20or%20agree%20with%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strategic%20importance%20of%20the%20Maldives%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20makes%20Male%20significant%20for%20Indian%20interests.%20Historical%20and%20cultural%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20peoples%20further%20reinforces%20this%20relationship%20where%20India%20has%20come%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20the%20Maldives%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20its%20neighborhood%20first%20approach.%20And%20like%20all%20nations%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20the%20wider%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%2C%20it%20is%20also%20well-accepted%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20China%20will%20be%20a%20key%20economic%20player%20for%20most%20nations.%20Often%20these%20nations%20will%20play%20Beijing%20against%20New%20Delhi%20and%20vice%20versa%20in%20order%20to%20get%20the%20best%20possible%20deals%20for%20them.%20Unlike%20China%2C%20India%20is%20often%20part%20of%20the%20domestic%20political%20landscape%20in%20most%20of%20its%20neighbours%2C%20thereby%20suffering%20from%20an%20inherent%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20crunch%2C%20it%20is%20India%20which%20is%20the%20first%20responder.%20Sri%20Lanka's%20economic%20crisis%20saw%20China%20maintaining%20a%20distance%20with%20India%20reacting%20fast%20and%20delivering%20help%20in%20real%20time.%20Muizzu%20has%20suggested%20that%20he%20is%20keen%20to%20reduce%20trade%20dependence%20on%20India%20by%20diversifying%20Maldivian%20food%20imports%20and%20overseas%20healthcare%20services.%20But%20many%20of%20the%20countries%20that%20he%20would%20seek%20to%20engage%20with%20are%20partners%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20India%20that%20has%20a%20web%20of%20partnerships%20across%20geographies%20that%20Muizzu%20would%20find%20difficult%20to%20ignore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20aim%2C%20however%2C%20is%20to%20mollycoddle%20China%2C%20then%20there%20are%20limits%20to%20what%20New%20Delhi%20can%20do%20to%20assuage%20Muizzu's%20concerns.%20If%2080-odd%20Indian%20soldiers%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20greater%20threat%20to%20Maldivian%20independence%20than%2037%20per%20cent%20share%20of%20China%20in%20Maldivian%20total%20debt%2C%20then%20it%20is%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Maldives%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20Muizzu's%20priorities.%20India%20would%20be%20much%20better%20off%20leaving%20the%20Muizzu%20government%20to%20its%20own%20devices%20and%20letting%20it%20learn%20the%20lessons%20that%20many%20other%20nations%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20beyond%20have%20learnt%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20Chinese%20embrace.%20India's%20strategic%20interests%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20affected%20much%20by%20bringing%20back%20its%20few%20soldiers%20from%20the%20Maldives%20but%20it%20is%20the%20long%20term%20trust%20between%20two%20close%20neighbors%20that%20Muizzu's%20actions%20has%20undermined%20that%20would%20be%20the%20biggest%20casualty%20of%20this%20shortsighted%20approach%20to%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20book%20is%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20Afghan%20Muddle%26quot%3B%20(HarperCollins)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705389240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fcblk2mq8_mohamed-muizzu-_625x300_07_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-should-let-maldives-learn-the-cost-of-a-chinese-embrace-4671859%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20strategic%20interests%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20affected%20much%20by%20bringing%20back%20its%20few%20soldiers%20from%20the%20Maldives%20but%20it%20is%20the%20long%20term%20trust%20between%20two%20close%20neighbors%20that%20Muizzu's%20actions%20has%20undermined%20that%20would%20be%20the%20biggest%20casualty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-should-let-maldives-learn-the-cost-of-a-chinese-embrace-4671859%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-should-let-maldives-learn-the-cost-of-a-chinese-embrace-4671859%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-should-let-maldives-learn-the-cost-of-a-chinese-embrace-4671859%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nihang%20Sikh%20kills%20man%20over%20'sacrilege'%20at%20gurdwara%20in%20Punjab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705389087000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106890596%2Cimgsize-55874.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Famritsar%2Fpunjab-nihang-sikh-