tory%20in%20Arkansas%20for%20their%20contribution%20to%20his%20country's%20security%20-%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20HIMARS%20multiple%20rocket%20launchers%20made%20there.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20that%20we%20take%20these%20messages%20not%20only%20to%20Washington%20but%20also%20to%20other%20part%20of%20American%20society%2C%20to%20states%20that%20are%20perhaps%20a%20little%20more%20conservative%2C%26quot%3B%20Margus%20Tsahkna%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outreach%20is%20just%20one%20example%20of%20how%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20are%20delicately%20-%20but%20urgently%20-%20preparing%20for%20Trump's%20possible%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20It's%20a%20reality%20that's%20likely%20to%20resonate%20at%20this%20week's%20meetings%20of%20the%20global%20elite%20in%20Davos%20after%20the%20former%20president's%20convincing%20win%20in%20the%20Iowa%20caucuses%20further%20tightened%20his%20grip%20on%20the%20Republican%20nomination%2C%20setting%20up%20a%20probable%20rematch%20with%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20lags%20in%20national%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202016%2C%20Trump's%20election%20stunned%20US%20allies%20and%20rivals%20alike.%20This%20time%2C%20leaders%20aren't%20taking%20any%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20Washington's%20Embassy%20Row%20have%20been%20scouring%20the%20city%20to%20meet%20ex-officials%20and%20anyone%20else%20close%20to%20the%20former%20president%20to%20get%20a%20read%20on%20his%20foreign%20policy%20plans.%20Some%20have%20even%20reached%20out%20directly%20to%20Trump%2C%20massaging%20his%20ego%2C%20or%20in%20Estonia's%20case%2C%20seeking%20to%20head%20off%20his%20habitual%20complaint%20that%20Europe%20isn't%20spending%20enough%20on%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20are%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20publicly.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clearly%20a%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20European%20Central%20Bank%20President%20Christine%20Lagarde%20told%20French%20TV%20last%20week%2C%20citing%20the%20lessons%20of%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20gestures%20outside%20a%20polling%20station%20after%20voting%20in%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%20New%20York%2C%20on%20Nov.%208%2C%202016%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20gestures%20outside%20a%20polling%20station%20after%20voting%20in%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%20New%20York%2C%20on%20Nov.%208%2C%202016%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjporo7io_donald-trump-bloomberg_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20gestures%20outside%20a%20polling%20station%20after%20voting%20in%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%20New%20York%2C%20on%20Nov.%208%2C%202016%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20in%20power%20are%20so%20open.%20But%20interviews%20with%20government%20officials%20from%20Europe%20to%20Asia%2C%20Africa%20and%20Latin%20America%20lay%20bare%20their%20concerns%20-%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20their%20hopes%20-%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20a%20Trump%20reprise%2C%20for%20security%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20climate%20action%2C%20and%20the%20balance%20of%20global%20power.%20Most%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20discussing%20what's%20nominally%20an%20internal%20US%20matter%2C%20with%20the%20campaign%20only%20now%20picking%20up%20and%20predicted%20to%20be%20tight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFears%2C%20Hopes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20US%20allies%20are%20concerned%20about%20Trump's%20America%20First%20rhetoric%20and%20threats%20to%20pull%20out%20of%20NATO%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20his%20protectionist%20trade%20policies.%20At%20European%20Union%20summits%2C%20some%20leaders%20are%20scared%20to%20even%20mention%20the%20prospect%20of%20his%20return%20for%20fear%20of%20making%20it%20more%20likely%2C%20one%20senior%20diplomat%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20heading%20into%20its%20third%20year%2C%202024%20could%20be%20a%20tipping%20point%20for%20Europe's%20security%2C%20said%20a%20Baltic%20official.%20In%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Trump's%20unquestioning%20embrace%20of%20Israel%20has%20some%20EU%20diplomats%20worried%20the%20Gaza%20war%20might%20worsen%2C%20fueling%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20refugees%20heading%20for%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20nations%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20see%20opportunities%20in%20the%20former%20president's%20more%20transactional%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20enjoyed%20a%20personal%20rapport%20with%20Trump%20and%20his%20government%20preferred%20the%20previous%20administration%20to%20Biden's%2C%20which%20has%20lectured%20New%20Delhi%20on%20human%20rights%20even%20as%20it%20has%20sought%20to%20enlist%20its%20support%20against%20China%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%20Their%20fondest%20hope%3A%20Trump%20picks%20Indian-American%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20as%20his%20running%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil%2C%20which%20assumed%20the%20Group%20of%2020%20presidency%20from%20India%2C%20sees%20President%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva's%20G-20%20plans%20for%20climate%20action%2C%20poverty%20reduction%20and%20reform%20of%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20as%20vulnerable%20to%20a%20resurgent%20Trump.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItaly's%20agenda%20for%20its%20G-7%20presidency%20is%20similarly%20affected%20by%20the%20specter%20of%20his%20return.%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20also%20faces%20a%20personal%20and%20political%20dilemma%2C%20having%20cheered%20on%20Trump%20while%20in%20opposition%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Washington%20in%202019%2C%20but%20in%20office%20cultivating%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20Biden.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20counter-intuitively%2C%20the%20view%20from%20Beijing%20is%20one%20of%20little%20change%20in%20the%20fundamental%20trajectory%20of%20China-US%20relations.%20Wang%20Yiwei%2C%20director%20of%20Renmin%20University's%20Institute%20of%20International%20Affairs%2C%20noted%20that%20tariffs%20levied%20during%20the%20Trump%20presidency%20remain%20in%20place%2C%20and%20despite%20positive%20signals%20from%20last%20year's%20presidential%20meeting%2C%20what%20he%20called%20the%20US%20containment%20of%20China%20hasn't%20changed%2C%20bringing%20%26quot%3Breal%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%20Worries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20China's%20economy%20would%20benefit%20modestly%20from%20one%20of%20Trump's%20signature%20initiatives%2C%20the%20imposition%20of%2010%25%20across-the-board%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20and%20the%20likely%20retaliation%20it%20would%20bring%2C%20according%20to%20estimates%20by%20Bloomberg%20Economics.%20US%20growth%20and%20employment%20would%20slow.%20Canada%20and%20especially%20Mexico%2C%20fellow%20signatories%20of%20the%20USMCA%20trade%20deal%2C%20would%20suffer%20disproportionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8649a64o_us-tariff-graph-bloomberg_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20business%20community%20sees%20the%20USMCA%20as%20an%20existential%20issue%20-%20and%20it's%20due%20for%20a%20joint%20review%20in%202026.%20Still%2C%20as%20a%20veteran%20of%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20took%20care%20to%20stay%20on%20good%20terms%20with%20him%20in%20public%20while%20his%20senior%20aides%20forged%20relationships%20with%20Trump's%20staff%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20That%20gives%20his%20team%20some%20confidence%20they%20can%20%26quot%3Bstick-handle%26quot%3B%20another%20Trump%20presidency%2C%20though%20no%20one%20pretends%20it%20would%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexican