ming%20that%20he%20got%20too%20clingy%20too%20quickly%2C%20showed%20off%20his%20money%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bkept%20talking%20about%20how%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20his%20bad%20side%2C%20especially%20when%20he%20was%20on%20business%20calls.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20post%2C%20many%20other%20women%20commented%2C%20sharing%20similar%20experiences%20or%20mentioning%20a%20past%20warning%20about%20his%20behaviour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20out%20with%20him%20a%20few%20times%20just%20over%20a%20year%20ago.%20He%20told%20me%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20hear%20until%20I%20slept%20with%20him%2C%20and%20then%20he%20ghosted...%20I'd%20steer%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20one%20woman%2C%20as%20per%20a%20screenshot%20provided%20in%20the%20legal%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20been%20posted%20here%20before.%20The%20poster%20said%20he%20sent%20her%20a%20slew%20of%20texts%20calling%20her%20names%20because%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20night%20with%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20D'Ambrosio%2C%20the%20woman%20who%20first%20posted%20about%20him%20did%20so%20with%20her%20real%20name%20but%20changed%20it%20to%20anonymous%20after%20his%20lawyers%20contacted%20her%20last%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705384560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fbgt6k0gg_chicago-man-sues-women-for-75-million-_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchicago-man-sues-27-women-for-defamation-over-clingy-and-ghosting-accusations-on-facebook-4871515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Chicago%20man%20is%20taking%20legal%20action%20against%2027%20women%2C%20seeking%20%2475%20million%20in%20damages%20following%20negative%20reviews%20posted%20on%20a%20Facebook%20page.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.