ms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-wary-world-girds-for-donald-trumps-return-to-the-white-house%2Famp_articleshow%2F106887227.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni's%20Simple%20Tip%20That%20Transformed%20Shivam%20Dube's%20Career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeen%20as%20the%20bonafide%20six-hitter%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20Shivam%20Dube%2C%20reaffirmed%20his%20credentials%20for%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20selection%2C%20mesmerising%20fand%20and%20experts%20with%20his%20twin%20half-centuries%20in%20the%20first%20two%20T20Is%20against%20Afghanistan.%C2%A0One%20of%20the%20biggest%20hitters%20when%20the%20spinners%20are%20in%20operation%2C%20Dube%20blazed%20away%20to%20scintillating%20fifties%20in%20the%20first%20two%20T20%20Internationals%20against%20Afghanistan%2C%20making%20a%20fairly%20good%20spin%20attack%20look%20pedestrian%20with%20his%20power-hitting.%20Dube%20also%20credited%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20for%20his%20heroics%20in%20the%20shortest%2C%20but%20what%20exactly%20was%20the%20mantra%20he%20was%20given%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20cricketer%20Abhinav%20Mukund%2C%20in%20a%20chat%20on%20Jio%20Cinema%2C%20claimed%20that%20Dhoni%20advised%20Dube%20against%20attacking%20the%20short%20ball%2C%20a%20tip%20that%20has%20done%20wonders%20for%20the%20left-handed%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20little%20birdie%20told%20me%20that%20Dube%20had%20a%20chat%20with%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20he%20told%20him%20-%20not%20rocket%20science%20-%20don't%20attack%20the%20short%20ball%2C%26quot%3B%20Mukund%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDube%2C%20in%20a%20chat%20with%20the%20broadcaster%20after%20the%20second%20T20I%2C%20gave%20insights%20into%20his%20preparation%20and%20approach%20to%20the%20game%2C%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20focussed%20only%20on%20the%20present%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pleasure%20to%20keep%20improving%20my%20performance%20as%20I%20am%20going%20along.%20The%20range%20I%20have%20is%20god's%20gift%20and%20I%20have%20also%20worked%20a%20lot%20on%20it.%20I%20have%20developed%20many%20areas%20of%20my%20game%20and%20I%20am%20getting%20the%20runs%20on%20the%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20Dube%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20way%20to%20his%20an%20unbeaten%2063%20off%2032%20balls%20in%20the%20second%20T20I%20here%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Dube%20smashed%20four%20towering%20sixes%20and%20five%20fours%2C%20as%20India%20chased%20down%20a%20target%20of%20173%20with%20as%20many%20as%2026%20balls%20to%20spare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20grabbing%20the%20headlines%20with%20the%20willow%20was%20the%20returning%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20hammered%20a%2034-ball%2068.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20think%20only%20about%20the%20present%20and%20not%20about%20the%20forthcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20Dube%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20I%20have%20thought%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20future.%20But%20I%20have%20realised%20that%20I%20got%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20present.%20I%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20my%20skills%2C%20so%20that's%20more%20important%20to%20me.%20I%20just%20try%20to%20keep%20myself%20grounded%20and%20try%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20I%20have%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20In%20stark%20contrast%20to%20his%20penchant%20to%20toy%20with%20the%20spinners%2C%2030-year-old%20Dube%20has%20often%20looked%20vulnerable%20against%20the%20short%20deliveries%20bowled%20at%20good%20pace.%20He%20admitted%20that%20the%20standard%20of%20fast%20bowlers%20in%20the%20IPL%20is%20much%20better%20than%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20that%20has%20gone%20into%20improving%20his%20game%20against%20short%20balls%2C%20Dube%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20worked%20a%20lot%20on%20it.%20When%20I%20was%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20dominate%20all%20the%20bowlers%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20IPL%20and%20Indian%20cricket%20it%20was%20not%20easy%20as%20bowlers%20were%20bowling%20over%20140km%2Fhr.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20worked%20a%20lot%20with%20side%20arms%2C%20but%20it%20is%20more%20about%20the%20mindset%20which%20I%20worked.%26quot%3B%20Dube%20had%20a%20poor%20start%20for%20India's%20white-ball%20team%20against%20Bangladesh%20more%20than%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20methods%20he%20has%20employed%20that's%20resulted%20in%20a%20significant%20improvement%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20credit%20goes%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20and%20Mahi%20bhai%20(MS%20Dhoni)%20because%20I%20always%20had%20this%20game%20in%20me.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20brought%20out%20the%20best%20in%20me.%20They%20have%20always%20encouraged%20me%20and%20said%20that%20they%20believe%20in%20me.%20Stephen%20Fleming%20and%20Mike%20Hussey%20have%20shown%20faith%20in%20me.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20about%20his%20mindset%20as%20a%20finisher%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20all-rounder%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20middle-order%20batsman%2C%20my%20role%20is%20to%20take%20on%20spinners%20and%20improve%20the%20strike%20rate.%20But%20when%20it%20is%20like%20getting%2020-25%20runs%2C%20I%20focus%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20have%20seen%20Mahi%20bhai%20do%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20am%20working%20in%20that%20direction.%20I%20have%20to%20keep%20myself%20calm%20and%20composed%20and%20just%20focus%20on%20one%20ball%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705383120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fc233fmbg_ms-dhoni-and-shivam-dube-bcci_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-t20i-2024%2Fthe-ms-dhoni-advice-that-turned-shivam-dube-into-a-star-performer-4866457%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shivam%20Dube's%20career%20resurrected%20ever%20since%20he%20was%20roped%20in%20by%20MS%20Dhoni-led%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salaar%20collects%20its%20lowest%20box%20office%20on%20Monday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705383115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106887143%2Cimgsize-15458.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fsalaar-collects-its-lowest-box-office-on-monday-looking-at-ending-its-run%2Farticleshow%2F106887211.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106887211.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPrabhas%20and%20Prashanth%20Neel's%20%26quot%3BSalaar%3A%20Part%201-%20Ceasefire%26quot%3B%20appears%20to%20be%20concluding%20its%20box%20office%20run%20with%20a%20Monday%20collection%20of%20just%20Rs%2055%20lakhs%2C%20marking%20its%20lowest%20earnings%20during%20its%20nearly%20one-month%20reign.%20Despite%20a%20strong%20start%2C%20the%20film's%20overall%20collection%20has%20gradually%20declined.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20way%20for%20Hrithik%20Roshan's%20%26quot%3BFighter%26quot%3B%20releasing%20next%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fsalaar-collects-its-lowest-box-office-on-monday-looking-at-ending-its-run%2Farticleshow%2F106887211.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Economists%20Say%20NITI%20Aayog%20Claims%20on%20Poverty%20Reduction%20Distort%20the%20Truth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16105531%2Findia-585078_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-01%2FMPI-22_NITI-Aayog20254.pdf%5C%22%3Enew%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2024.8%20crore%20people%20have%20been%20lifted%20out%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202022-23%2C%20experts%20of%20the%20economy%20have%20raised%20doubts%20over%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multidimensional%20measure%20looks%20at%20the%20areas%20covered%20in%20the%2012%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20across%20health%2C%20education%20and%20standard%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMultidimensional%20poverty%20in%20India%20was%20found%20to%20decline%20from%2029.17%25%20in%202013-14%20to%2011.28%25%20in%202022-23%20with%20about%2024.82%20crore%20people%20escaping%20poverty%20during%20this%20period.%20At%20the%20States%E2%80%99%20level%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20topped%20the%20list%20with%205.94%20crore%20people%20escaping%20poverty%20followed%20by%20Bihar%20at%203.77%20crore%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20at%202.30%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20claims%20that%20some%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Poshan%20Abhiyan%2C%20Anaemia%20Mukt%20Bharat%2C%20Ujjwala%20and%20others%20%E2%80%93%20have%20played%20%E2%80%9Ca%20crucial%20role%E2%80%9D%20in%20addressing%20different%20aspects%20of%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20says%20that%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20achieve%20the%20SDG%20of%20%E2%80%9Chalving%20multidimensional%20poverty%E2%80%9D%20well%20before%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20tweeted%20about%20the%20government%20think-tank%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20saying%2C%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CVery%20encouraging%2C%20reflecting%20our%20commitment%20towards%20furthering%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20focusing%20on%20transformative%20changes%20to%20our%20economy.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20towards%20all-round%20development%20and%20to%20ensure%20a%20prosperous%20future%20for%20every%20Indian.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fniti-aayog-makes-huge-poverty-relief-claim-several-economists-raise-objections%2Fcid%2F1994004%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20experts%20have%20raised%20some%20serious%20doubts%20over%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Multidimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20(MPI)%20to%20make%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20MPI%20simply%20tells%20us%20the%20percentage%20of%20people%20unable%20to%20access%20certain%20facilities%20provided%20by%20the%20government%20or%20(that%20are)%20available%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20retired%20Indian%20Economic%20Services%20officer%20K.L.%20Datta%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20used%20by%20planners%20and%20policymakers%20to%20fix%20targets%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20used%20as%20an%20input%20to%20make%20plans%20for%20poverty%20reduction.%20To%20sum%20up%2C%20the%20MPI%20does%20not%20represent%20poverty.%20The%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20project%20the%20MPI%20estimate%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20poverty%20ratio.%20This%20is%20not%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Sunil%20Ray%2C%20former%20director%20of%20the%20A.N.%20Sinha%20Institute%2C%20Patna%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20a%20nation%20achieve%20SDG%20when%20its%20government%20has%20to%20ensure%20the%20survival%20of%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20its%20population%20%5Bthrough%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%5D%3F%20The%20government%20is%20giving%20this%20freebie%20because%20the%20people%20are%20not%20self-dependent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomist%20and%20rights%20activist%20Jean%20Dr%C3%A8ze%20also%20expressed%20reservations%20about%20the%20use%20of%20the%20MPI.%20%E2%80%9C(The)%20MPI%20does%20not%20include%20any%20indicator%20of%20short-term%20purchasing%20power.%20Thus%2C%20we%20must%20read%20MPI%20data%20along%20with%20other%20information%2C%20including%20recent%20evidence%20of%20sluggish%20growth%20in%20real%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMPI%20data%20can%20complement%20but%20not%20substitute%20for%20poverty%20estimates%20from%20consumer%20expenditure%20surveys%20that%20are%20long%20overdue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsis%20Banerjee%2C%20economist%20and%20former%20vice-chancellor%20of%20Calcutta%20University%2C%20added%20that%20while%20the%20MPI%20could%20not%20be%20used%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20poverty%2C%20this%20particular%20government%20also%20cannot%20take%20credit%20for%20a%20reduced%20MPI.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20(MPI)%20has%20been%20declining%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20now%20and%20not%20just%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20Most%20studies%20show%20the%20credit%20for%20this%20goes%20to%20measures%20initiated%20before%20the%20change%20of%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202014%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6there%20is%20the%20big%20mystery%20as%20to%20why%20there%20has%20been%20a%20slide%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20performance%20on%20the%20World%20Hunger%20Index%20in%20recent%20times%20if%20there%20has%20been%20such%20impressive%20reductions%20in%20poverty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-ranks-111th-among-125-countries-in-global-hunger-index-report%5C%22%3Ewas%20ranked%20111%20among%20125%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20report%20released%20by%20two%20European%20agencies%20on%20October%2012%2C%202023.%20The%20only%20countries%20ranking%20lower%20than%20India%20were%20Timor-Leste%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Haiti%2C%20Guinea-Bissau%2C%20Liberia%2C%20Sierra%20Leone%2C%20Chad%2C%20Niger%2C%20Lesotho%2C%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%2C%20Yemen%2C%20Madagascar%2C%