20referred%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-state%20solution%2C%20where%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20able%20to%20live%20freely%20in%20an%20independent%20country%20within%20secure%20borders%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20avoid%20provocative%20and%20escalatory%20actions%2C%20and%20to%20facilitate%20movement%20towards%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20connectivity%20high%20on%20the%20agenda%2C%20Jaishankar%20asserted%20that%20India%20wanted%20to%20benefit%20from%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cunique%20geographical%20position%20to%20access%20markets%20in%20Central%20Asia%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Eurasia%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChabahar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20calling%20for%20re-energising%20the%20International%20North%20South%20Transport%20Corridor%2C%20the%20Indian%20minister%20also%20reiterated%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20developing%20the%20Iranian%20port%20of%20Chabahar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20importance%20of%20this%20project%20for%20both%20nations%2C%20I%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20monitor%20its%20progress%20under%20the%20direct%20supervision%20of%20the%20political%20leadership%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20indicated%20that%20discussions%20were%20held%20on%20the%20draft%20agreement%20on%20Chabahar%20which%20will%20talk%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20port%20for%20next%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Indian%20minister%20only%20referred%20to%20discussions%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIRNA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20that%20the%20text%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.irna.ir%2Fnews%2F85355146%2FIran-India-re