%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20they%20positively%20assessed%20the%20developments%20in%20bilateral%20relations%20and%20agreed%20to%20develop%20a%20roadmap%20for%20future%20initiatives%20to%20further%20%E2%80%9Cstrengthen%20the%20India-Russia%20special%20and%20privileged%20strategic%20partnership%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20conveying%20his%20best%20wishes%20for%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20presidency%20of%20BRICS%20in%202024%2C%20Modi%20assured%20Putin%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20full%20support.%20They%20also%20exchanged%20views%20on%20regional%20and%20global%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20note%20from%20the%20Kremlin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fkremlin.ru%2Fevents%2Fpresident%2Fnews%2F73270%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CVladimir%20Putin%20and%C2%A0%C2%A0Narendra%20Modi%20expressed%20interest%20in%20further%20intensifying%20mutually%20beneficial%20bilateral%20ties%20and%20wished%20each%20other%20success%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20presidential%20in%20Russia%20and%20parliamentary%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%2C%20according%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20note%2C%20discussed%20cooperation%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20trade%2C%20economic%2C%20scientific%20and%20technical%20cooperation%2C%20energy%2C%20transport%20and%20logistics%2C%20and%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Russian%20Far%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20note%20also%20said%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20chairmanship%20of%20BRICS%20this%20year%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Cemphasised%20their%20readiness%20to%20closely%20coordinate%20approaches%20across%20the%20entire%20large-scale%20agenda%20of%20the%20association%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20%E2%80%9Ca%20number%20of%20other%20international%20topics%20%5Bwere%5D%20also%20touched%20upon%2C%20including%20the%20situation%20around%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20M