20Court%20as%20criminal%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20political%20organisations%20who%20believe%20in%20Hindutva.%20The%20land%20was%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20same%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20building%20a%20temple.%20Yet%20again%20political%20organisations%20have%20taken%20over%20and%20want%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20The%20role%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20as%20a%20political%20organisation%20is%20understandable%20but%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20involved%20the%20entire%20government%20paraphernalia%20in%20this%20process.%20The%20money%20being%20spent%20to%20make%20it%20a%20special%20event%20is%20sheer%20madness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20when%20did%20it%20become%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20job%20to%20build%20temples%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20which%20abides%20by%20a%20secular%20constitution%3F%20The%20prime%20minister%20is%20going%20around%20as%20the%20chief%20priest%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20God%20created%20humans.%20But%20consider%20the%20arrogance%20of%20Brahminical%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20probably%20the%20only%20such%20religion%20on%20earth%2C%20which%20believes%20it%20can%20infuse%20life%20into%20a%20God%E2%80%99s%20statue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Last%20year%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20lit%2022.23%20lakh%20earthen%20lamps%20in%20Ayodhya%20during%20%E2%80%98Deepotsav%E2%80%99%2C%20something%20started%20by%20him%20after%20he%20assumed%20the%20post.%20He%20even%20bettered%20his%20own%20record%20of%20lighting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-ayodhya-mythical-ram-sita-touch-down-in-helicopter-for-grand-diwali-celebrations%2Fstory-gMzvD3q6GN6U6nDYTV2luK.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3E17%20lakh%20lamps%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGuinness%20Book%20of%20World%20Records%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20colossal%20wastage%20makes%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20whom%20are%20in%20his%20state%2C%20who%20come%20the%20next%20morning%20to%20collect%20unburnt%20mustard%20oil%20from%20these%20lamps%20to%20use%20for%20cooking.%20What%20is%20being%20achieved%20by%20burning%20these%20lamps%3F%20Why%20should%20the%20government%20be%20obsessed%20with%20world%20records%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20previous%20record%20is%20also%20in%20its%20name%3F%20If%20this%20is%20not%20insanity%20then%20what%20is%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20Adityanath%20also%20paid%20professional%20models%20to%20dress%20up%20as%20Ram%2C%20Laxman%2C%20and%20Sita%20and%20provided%20them%20with%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-ayodhya-mythical-ram-sita-touch-down-in-helicopter-for-grand-diwali-celebrations%2Fstory-gMzvD3q6GN6U6nDYTV2luK.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Egovernment%20helicopter%20to%20recreate%20the%20scene%20of%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20return%20from%20Lanka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Is%20this%20not%20a%20misuse%20of%20government%20assets%3F%20All%20this%20when%20the%20life%20of%20people%20has%20been%20made%20difficult%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F23143324%2F275075675_1743511045991589_5709126568863000856_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F23143324%2F275075675_1743511045991589_5709126568863000856_n.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F23143324%2F275075675_1743511045991589_5709126568863000856_n-300x219.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-588266%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22657%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FMYogiAdityanath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20Convicts%20in%20the%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%2C%20released%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20have%20been%20ordered%20to%20be%20put%20back%20in%20jail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20But%20nobody%20knows%20whether%20they%E2%80%99ll%20actually%20go%20to%20jail%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20due%20this%20year.%20The%20female%20wrestlers%20protesting%20against%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20justice.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20maintain%20a%20stranglehold%20over%20the%20wrestling%20administration%20in%20India.%20Two%20male%20wrestlers%20have%20also%20returned%20their%20medals%20and%20awards%20in%20a%20strong%20rebuke%20to%20the%20government.%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%2C%20who%20instigated%20his%20son%20to%20drive%20his%20vehicle%20over%20farmers%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20killing%20four%20of%20them%20and%20a%20journalist%2C%20still%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20home%20department.%20While%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20await%20justice%2C%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20son%20roams%20free.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E4.%20Street%20vendors%E2%80%99%20carts%20from%20the%20Lanka%20market%20outside%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20have%20been%20confiscated%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20and%2C%20unlike%20previous%20occasions%2C%20will%20not%20release%20them%20without%20police%20permission.%20Requests%20to%20the%20police%20commissioner%20have%20gone%20unheard.%20This%2C%20despite%20a%202014%20street%20vendor%E2%80%99s%20law%20which%20makes%20it%20illegal%20for%20the%20police%20and%20municipal%20corporation%20employees%20to%20remove%20street%20vendors%20without%20their%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E5.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Ramnagar%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20stay%20orders%20from%20the%20court%2C%20houses%20were%20demolished%20in%20a%20road%20widening%20exercise.%20The%20circle%20rates%20in%20Varanasi%20district%20have%20not%20been%20updated%20since%202019%20so%20when%20land%20is%20acquired%20from%20farmers%20in%20Pindra%20for%20the%20Kashi%20Dwar%20project%2C%20farmers%20will%20not%20get%20fair%20compensation.%20In%20Azamgarh%2C%20farmers%20from%20eight%20villages%20have%20been%20opposing%20a%20proposed%20international%20airport%20project%20questioning%20its%20need%20when%20there%20is%20one%20just%20two%20hours%20away%20in%20Varanasi.%20The%20farmers%20are%2C%20in%20general%2C%20unhappy%20with%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flittle-known-about-mughal-era-mosque-in-up-where-muslim-youth-was-booked-for-offering-azaan%5C%22%3ELittle%20Known%20About%20Mughal-Era%20%E2%80%98Mosque%E2%80%99%20in%20UP%20Where%20Muslim%20Youth%20Was%20Booked%20for%20Offering%20Azaan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E6.%20The%20farmers%20in%20Hardoi%2C%20Unnao%2C%20Sitapur%20and%20most%20of%20U.P.%20have%20to%20keep%20awake%20all%20night%20to%20save%20their%20crops%20from%20stray%20cattle.%20The%20government%20claims%20to%20provide%20Rs.%2050%20per%20cattle%20per%20day%20to%20feed%20them%20but%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20dedicated%20budget%20to%20build%20cow%20sheds.%20Hence%2C%20most%20gram%20pradhans%2C%20like%20the%20one%20from%20Gram%20Sabha%20Mahua%20Danda%20in%20Hardoi%20District%20try%20to%20shirk%20their%20responsibility.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20local%20Sandila%20MLA%2C%20belonging%20to%20his%20own%20caste%2C%20is%20supporting%20him%20against%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20chief%20secretary%20to%20put%20all%20stray%20cattle%20in%20cow%20sheds%20and%20%3Cem%3Egaushalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20farmers%20suffer%20and%20some%20have%20even%20given%20up%20agriculture%20as%20the%20UP%20government%20has%20made%20it%20illegal%20to%20fence%20their%20fields%20with%20bladed%20wires.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E7.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20come%20up%20with%20an%20ingenious%20way%20of%20avoiding%20increase%20in%20Urea%20fertiliser%E2%80%99s%20rates.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Ffertiliser-minister-says-neem-coated-urea-available-at-rs-266-5%2F45-kg-bag-asks-sp-prez-not-to-mislead-farmers%2Farticleshow%2F106727977.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20They%20have%20simply%20reduced%20the%20quantity%20of%20Urea%20in%20a%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2050%20kg%20to%2040%20kg%2C%20in%20two%20instalments%2C%20without%20changing%20the%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E8.%20The%20Gram%20Sabha%20of%20Aseni%20in%20Barabanki%20passed%20a%20resolution%20against%20liquor%20shops%20in%20the%20village%20in%202021.%20However%2C%20district%20officials%20said%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20state%20policy%20and%20lathi-charged%20a%20demonstration%20demanding%20their%20closure.%20Under%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20foreign%20liquor%20shops%20are%20doing%20brisk%20business.%20However%2C%20liquor%20shops%20have%20been%20ordered%20shut%20only%20for%20January%2022%2C%20exposing%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E9.%20All%20contractual%20employees%20like%20para-teachers%20are%20agitating%20against%20the%20government%20for%20regularisation%20of%20their%20jobs%20or%20at%20least%20an%20increase%20in%20their%20modest%20honoraria.%20Just%20before%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20in%20UP%20in%202022%2C%20an%20aspirant%20for%20a%20government%20teaching%20post%2C%20Shikha%20Pal%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahmedabadmirror.com%2Fjob-seeker-has-been-sitting-atop-water-tank-for-past-120-days%2F81814466.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20sat%20atop%20a%20water%20tank%20at%20the%20education%20directorate%20for%20about%20half%20a%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20protesting%20against%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20recruitment%20policy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E10.%20Additionally%2C%20Rs%2010%20postal%20orders%2C%20which%20are%20required%20to%20file%20an%20application%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%20have%20disappeared%20from%20post%20offices%20across%20UP%20%E2%80%93%20Lucknow%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Barabanki%2C%20Moradabad%20and%20Varanasi%20%E2%80%93%20so%20that%20people%20cannot%20hold%20the%20government%20accountable%20by%20asking%20uncomfortable%20questions.%20This%20is%20symbolic%20of%20suppression%20of%20all%20dissent%20in%20BJP%20rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20not%20going%20to%20bring%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20UP%20or%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20At%20best%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20help%20ensure%20a%20political%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20the%20consecration%20is%20happening%20even%20before%20the%20construction%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20temple.%20It%20is%20a%20political%20temple.%20It%20is%20a%20project%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20organisations%20which%20has%20succeeded%20because%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20power.%20Some%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20are%20unsure%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20invitation%20for%20the%20consecration.%20They%20should%20outrightly%20reject%20it%20as%20it%20is%20a%20BJP%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20Hindutva%20organisations%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20No%20senior%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20or%20BJP%20leader%20has%20ever%20written%20a%20book%20on%20Hindu%20religion%20like%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Vinoba%20Bhave%2C%20Sarvapalli%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20Aurobindo%20Ghosh%2C%20etc%2C%20have%20done.%20Hence%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20feel%20guilty%20about%20not%20being%20part%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20voters%20need%20to%20distinguish%20between%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESandeep%20Pandey%20is%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20Socialist%20Party%20(India).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705325299000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11102438%2FScreenshot-2024-01-11-at-10.24.0.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F10-things-the-bjp-wants-you-to-overlook-while-it-misdirects-focus-on-the-ram-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20clear%20that%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20not%20going%20to%20bring%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20UP%20or%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F10-things-the-bjp-wants-you-to-overlook-while-it-misdirects-focus-on-the-ram-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20brothers%20raided%20Swiss%20museum%20'to%20clear%20a%20debt'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705325257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3E26%2Fproduction%2F_132301951_screenshot2024-01-14164529.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67950947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stewart%20and%20Louis%20Ahearne%20admitted%20being%20part%20of%20a%20gang%20which%20raided%20a%20museum%20in%20Geneva.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67950947%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https